quran[28{c,v,t}:
69,35,lehaza aaj nah yahan iss ka koi yaar gham khawar hai
69,36,aur nah zakhamo ke dhowan ke siwa iss ke liye koi khana
69,37,jisay khata karon ke siwa koi nahi khata
69,38,"pas nahi, mein qasam khata hon unn cheezon ki bhi jo tum dekhte ho"
69,39,aur unn ki bhi jinhein tum nahi dekhte
69,40,yeh aik rasool kareem ka qoul hai
69,41,"kisi shayar ka qoul nahi hai, tum log kam hi imaan laatay ho"
69,42,"aur nah yeh kisi kahanka qoul hai, tum log kam hi ghhor karte ho"
69,43,yeh rab alaalmin ki taraf se nazil howa hai
69,44,aur agar is ( nabi ) ne khud ghurr kar koi baat hamari taraf mansoob ki hoti
69,45,to hum iss ka dayan haath pakar letay
69,46,aur iss ki rug gardan kaat daaltay
69,47,phir tum mein se koi ( hamein ) is kaam se roknay wala nah hota
69,48,dar haqeeqat yeh parhaizgaar logon ke liye aik nasiyaat hai
69,49,aur hum jantay hain ke tum mein se kuch log jhutlanay walay hain
69,50,aisay kafiroon ke liye yaqeenan yeh mojab hasrat hai
69,51,aur yeh bilkul yakeeni haq hai
69,52,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, apne rab azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo"
70,1,"mangnay walay ne azaab manga hai, ( woh azaab ) jo zaroor waqay honay wala hai"
70,2,"kafiroon ke liye hai, koi ussay dafaa karne wala nahi"
70,3,uss khuda ki taraf se hai jo urooj ke zeeno ka maalik hai
70,4,mulaika aur rooh uss ke huzoor charh kar jatay hain aik aisay din mein jis ki miqdaar pachaas hazaar saal hai
70,5,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, sabr karo, shaista sabr"
70,6,yeh log ussay daur samajte hain
70,7,aur hum usay qareeb dekh rahay hain
70,8,( woh azaab uss roz hoga ) jis roz aasman pighli hui chandi ki terhan ho jaye ga
70,9,aur pahar rang barang ke dhunkayhue oon(wool) jaisay ho jayen ge
70,10,aur koi jigaree dost apne jigaree dost ko nah pouchye ga
